    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, likely requiring significant repairs or serving as a parts car. The engine struggles to start and runs roughly, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is significant rust and several dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with non-functional electronics. It is priced to reflect its current state and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
