      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that balances performance with proven reliability. This unit has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring mechanical integrity and a refined driving experience. Featuring a clean aesthetic and a well-appointed interior, it represents an exceptional value proposition for the discerning motorist seeking quality without compromise.",
